7. SUMMARY AND REMARKS

This  system is word  oriented written using MOL.  The system's intention is to
serve experienced users of mailboxes.

If you think, MYSTERY-SYSTEMS is too sophisticated for you, please try another
mailbox!

If you have some troubles or special questions, please write a mail to SYSOP.

